tosdr.case: The service warns you of the potential consequences related to third-party access

title: The service warns you of the potential consequences related to third-party access
quoteText:
This site may contain embedded content from other services, including (without limitation) YouTube, Twitter, Facebook and Reddit.
We do not share data with these services, but they may collect additional information about you, such as the videos that you watch which are embedded on this site but provided by their service.
